      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, known for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains composed with sharp turn-in and excellent lateral stability. Essential preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system overhaul and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement, mitigating common platform weaknesses. It offers a tactile driving experience with a linear power band and a resonant metallic exhaust note characteristic of M-division engineering.",
